 Zendaya Photo Glamour Euphoria actress Zendaya stars in her first-ever Super Bowl ad. The 25-year old actress makes her Super Bowl ad debut starring in the ad for website building company Squarespace. With the full advertisement scheduled to air until Super Bowl Sunday on February 13, the company shared a sun-filled, 10-second teaser clip on Twitter on Thursday. The teaser titled “Everything to Shell… Sell Anything” starts with a close-up sot of a seashell before spiralling out to show Zendaya spinning in a blue halter dress. Turning to face the camera, she reveals a sea-inspired look. The actress wears a turquoise dress adorned with pearls, shells and sea stars on the bodice as she walks away from the camera with seagulls, crashing waves setting the mood. Adweek reports that Zendaya’s ad should air in the first quarter of the Super Bowl. See the trailer HERE: 2.13.22 #Squarespace presents: Everything to S̶h̶e̶l̶l̶ Sell Anything. Starring #Zendaya … stay tuned for more.  #BigGame pic.twitter.com/8xGlyeHdLz — Squarespace (@squarespace) February 3, 2022